Following suggestions might be helpful,
1. I guess you have to build tensor flow from its source in order to use those instructions and make faster computations.
2. Visit this link as well for same issue [https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/7778](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/7778)
3. Please review guidelines before [https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/ISSUE_TEMPLATE.md](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/ISSUE_TEMPLATE.md) posting an issue.
